RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT DISTINCT a.CONTRACT_REF_NO,a.CONTRACT_CCY,a.COUNTERPARTY,b.maturity_date,a.AUTH_STATUS,a.CONTRACT_STATUS, a.USER_DEFINED_STATUS,a.BRANCH,a.DEPARTMENT_CODE,a.TREASURY_SOURCE,a.LATEST_EVENT_SEQ_NO,c.customer_name1 FROM OLTBS_CONTRACT a, oltbs_contract_master b, oltms_customer c WHERE a.BRANCH = GLOBAL.CURRENT_BRANCH AND a.MODULE_CODE = 'OL' AND a.CONTRACT_STATUS IN ('A', 'L') AND a.CONTRACT_REF_NO = b.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND a.LATEST_VERSION_NO = b.VERSION_NO AND a.COUNTERPARTY = c.customer_no ORDER BY a.CONTRACT_REF_NO

SELECT DISTINCT TO_CHAR(DUE_DATE,'YYYY-MM-DD') DUE_DATE FROM OLTBS_AMOUNT_DUE A WHERE CONTRACT_REF_NO = ? AND INFLOW_OUTFLOW = CASE WHEN COMPONENT ='PRINCIPAL' THEN 'I' ELSE INFLOW_OUTFLOW END AND (NVL(AMOUNT_DUE, 0) -(NVL(AMOUNT_SETTLED, 0) + NVL(ADJUSTED_AMOUNT, 0))) > 0 AND 'Y' <> (SELECT Olpks_Servicesy.Fn_Is_Ristourne_Component(a.COMPONENT, ?) FROM DUAL) ORDER BY DUE_DATE
SELECT distinct A.CPTY,A.cust_name FROM OLVWS_PYMNT_SMRY A WHERE A.AUTHSTATUS = 'A' AND A.CONTRACTSTATUS = 'A' ORDER BY A.CPTY
